msgid "front_page_text"
msgstr "<p>&nbsp;</p><p>This is no more up to date! See french version...</p><p>The application integrates the management of incoming mail:</p><ul><li>Automatic creation of incoming mail from scanned files with a separator barcode stuck on the first page of every mail</li><li>Completion of incoming mail with preview of the scanned document and drag / drop from the extracted text by OCR</li><li>Without automatic injection from the scanner, the ability to create a mail and manually link the scanned document (for example, if the format is particular)</li><li>Predefined searches following actions to take and state of mails</li><li>Results display in a dynamic table with changeable fields filters, sorting, pagination, actions column, batch actions, etc.</li><li>Contact management (senders, recipients)</li><li>Choice of treating service, copy services and task management (that can be assigned to other services)</li><li>Choice of a responsible user in the treating service or on a task and also a due date</li><li>Mail validation workflow</li><li>Mail treatment workflow</li><li>Possibility to advance element by element from a search results</li><li>etc.</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p>"

